American MedicalInternational said it intends to repurchase from time to timeon the open market up to 150 mln dlrs of its common stock andplans to spend another 250 mln dlrs in reducing long-term debt.    It said it would spend about 100 mln dlrs on debt maturingin 1989.    American Medical said funding for the program will comefrom cash flow and from the divestiture and restructuring ofcorporate assets. Reuter&#3;